title: Japan creates multibillion-dollar space strategic fund to boost space industry
summary: Japan has established a multibillion-dollar Space Strategic Fund to help develop the country’s innovation, autonomy and international competitiveness in space.

title: Rocket Lab launches Synspective radar imaging satellite
summary: Rocket Lab launched a radar imaging satellite for Japanese company Synspective March 12, the latest in a series of launches for that company.
